@chapter Fundamentals

This chapter isolates the individual parts of the @file{readargs} library.

@menu
* raOpt object::   defines an option's invocation and action
* raAgent object:: base struct of object that processes an option
* raScene object:: holds the static program data (defined options and user arguments)
* raCache object:: gives access to and tracks progress through command line arguments
@end menu

